com.poesys.ms.col

Class NullColumnValueImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.poesys.ms.col.NullColumnValueImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IColumnValue<java.lang.Integer>, java.io.Serializable

    public class NullColumnValueImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable, IColumnValue<java.lang.Integer>
    An implementation of the IColumnValue interface that represents a null column value that has a specific JDBC data type. Note that this is not currently used by messaging as all messages required non-null columns in an active primary key; this implementation exists for completeness.
    Author:
    Robert J. Muller
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
